** GORGEOUS DUPLEX- AVAILABLE 9/1/22** Features classic charm with many modern updates including central a/c. Step across the lovely sitting porch to the front door which opens to a spacious foyer, currently used as a kids play room. The Foyer opens directly to the large living room with front bay window or to the main hall servicing the first floor master, main bathroom with double vanity, and stair to the second floor bedrooms. Through the living room is a large formal dining room, complete with wainscoting, followed by the second full bathroom and updated kitchen. Just off the kitchen is the rear entry, which doubles as a butler's pantry with bar sink and high storage shelves. The rear door opens to a second shared porch, patio, and garden. 1 assigned garage parking space in the 2 car detached garage is included in the rent. Pet Negotiable!  The large unfinished basement provides plenty of storage space, as well as in unit laundry with newer large capacity machines. BROKER FEE REQUIRED!<br>
